    <title>Work | Creative Technologist</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/estilo.min.css">
</head>

<body>

    <main>
        <!-- @import "header" -->
        <section class="portfolio-hero">
            <div class="portfolio-texto">
                <span class="etiqueta">PORTFOLIO</span>
                <h1>Our Projects</h1>
                <p>A collection of projects that we worked as UX/UI designers, ranging from mobile applications to
                    digital product interfaces. Each project reflects unique challenges and thoughtful, user-centered
                    design solutions.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="featured-section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <span class="etiqueta">SPOTLIGHT</span>
                <h2>Projects Under Construction</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="featured-grid">

                <article class="work-card">
                    <div class="work-image">
                        <img src="https://cdn.britannica.com/34/267034-050-91CC3AFB/Pinterest-logo.jpg"
                            alt="E-Commerce Platform Preview">
                        <span class="badge stack-blue">UX/UI</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="work-content">
                        <div class="work-meta">
                            <span><i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i> 2025</span>
                            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-users"></i> 2 designers</span>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Pinterest Chat Bot</h3>
                        <p>Designing a Pinterest-inspired chatbot focused on enhancing content discovery through a
                            conversational and intuitive interface. The project explores how AI-driven interactions can
                            simplify search, inspiration, and user engagement within a visual platform.</p>

                        <div class="skill-tags">
                            <span>Figma</span><span>React</span>
                        </div>

                        <div class="work-stats">
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <span class="stat-value">10K+</span>
                                <span class="stat-label">USERS</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <span class="stat-value">99.9%</span>
                                <span class="stat-label">UPTIME</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="stat-item">
                                <span class="stat-value">4.8</span>
                                <span class="stat-label">RATING</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="work-links">
                            <h5> To be published...</h5>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="work-card">
                    <div class="work-image">
